    +lead-in({
        content: `A data sheet is an informational document that outlines the technical specifications of a product, component, or software program. It spells out the performance and constraints of the system and its components. Its purpose is to help experienced technical professionals arrive at a buying decision by presenting them with sufficient information to satisfy their questions, or to seek additional information from white papers, brochures, or user guides. Data sheets ultimately lead to a more informed and confident purchasing decision for buyers. `,
