    article(class=" page-content mt-10 lg:mt-20 xl:mt-24 leading-normal overflow-hidden")
        .container.flow-root
            p.drop-cap(style="--color: hsla(207, 100%, 39%, 1)") As the world leader in satellite communications, Cobham is constantly releasing new products featuring industry-leading technologies. Decision-makers across multiple industries seek to understand these products and their place within the satellite communications eco-system.

            -
                const datasheetReferred = [
                    "Specifications Sheet",
                    "Features Document",
                    "Specs",
                    "Engineering Data",
                    "Technical Summary"
                ]

            div(class="md:float-right my-5 mx-auto md:m-5 lg:m-8 text-base text-center font-proxima-bold leading-tight max-w-sm lg:max-w-max border-2 border-blue-light fade-in-left")
                div(class=" bg-blue-light text-white px-8 lg:px-12.5 py-4" ) Data sheet are also referred to as:
                each name, index in datasheetReferred
